metadata.description: Kokonaisvaltainen raportti indivisible stochastic processes tutkimuksesta

executive_summary.research_question: Voivatko hybridijärjestelmät tuottaa indivisible stochastic process -käyttäytymistä?

metadata.description: Vaihe 2: Satunnaisuustyyppi-analyysi ja optimaalisten parametrien löytäminen

research_summary.title: Indivisible Stochastic Processes from Hybrid Systems
research_summary.hypothesis: Can hybrid systems (RMT + fractals + percolation) naturally evolve indivisible stochastic process structures?
research_summary.methodology: 3-phase systematic investigation with validation, randomness screening, and parameter optimization

scientific_significance.quantum_mechanics_interpretation: Supports Barandes indivisible stochastic processes theory
scientific_significance.measurement_problem: Potentially resolved - no wave function collapse needed

methodological_contributions.parameter_optimization: Grid search with indivisible score metric

future_research: Bell inequality tests with hybrid models
